help: Spawns the specified custom star systems in this current Sector map. If "all" is entered as the first argument, spawns all currently-loaded custom star systems to the Sector map, while respecting any "isEnabled" options. Otherwise, the specified custom star systems will spawn even if their "isEnabled" option is set to false.
Lists the IDs of all currently-loaded custom star systems from the merged customStarSystem.json.
